<pb ed="X" id="X10.0256.0435c" n="0435c"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c01"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c02"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c03"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a01"/><ab type='juan' subtype='open'>大方廣圓覺脩多羅了義經略疏注序</ab><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c04"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c05"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a02"/><byline>唐終南山草堂寺沙門　宗密　述</byline><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c06"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a03"/><byline>龍沙章江禪院沙門如山註序</byline><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c07"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a04"/><div type='' level='2'><ab type="prose">。</ab><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c09"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a06"/><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">元享利貞乾之德也始於一氣常樂我淨佛之德也<lb
 ed="X" n="0435c10"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a07"/>本乎一心。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">專一氣而致柔脩一心而成道。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">心也者冲虗妙粹炳煥靈明無去無<lb
 ed="X" n="0435c14"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a11"/>來冥通三際非中非外洞徹十方。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">不滅不生豈四山之可害離性離相奚五色之能<lb
 ed="X" n="0435c16"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a13"/>盲。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">處生死流驪珠獨耀於滄海。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">踞涅槃岸桂輪孤朗於碧天。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0435c19"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a16"/><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">大矣哉萬法資始也<lb
 ed="X" n="0435c20"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929a17"/>萬法虗偽緣會而生。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">生法本無一切唯<lb
 ed="X" n="0435c22"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b01"/>識識如幻夢但是一心心寂而知目之圓覺彌滿清<lb
 ed="X" n="0435c23"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b02"/>淨中不容他。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">故德用無邊皆同一性性起<pb ed="X" id="X10.0256.0436a" n="0436a"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0436a01"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b04"/>為相境智歷然相得性融身心廓爾方之海印越彼<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a02"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b05"/>太虗恢󳭪焉晃晃焉逈出思議之表也。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">我佛證此憫物迷<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a04"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b07"/>之再歎奇哉三思大事。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">既全十力能<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a06"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b09"/>摧樹下魔軍。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">爰起四心欲示宅中寶<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a07"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b10"/>藏。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">然迷頭捨父悟有易難。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">故仙苑覺場教興頓漸。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">漸設五時之異<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a11"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b14"/>空有迭彰頓無二諦之殊幽靈絕待今此經者頓之<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a12"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0929b15"/>類歟。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">故如來入寂光土凡聖一源現受用身主伴同<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a16"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930a01"/>會。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">曼殊大<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a17"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930a02"/>士創問本起之因薄伽至尊首提究竟之果。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">照斯真體<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a19"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930a04"/>滅彼夢形知無我人誰受輪轉。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">種種幻化生於覺心<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a21"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930a06"/>幻盡覺圓心通法徧。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">心本是佛由念起而漂沉岸實不移因舟行而<lb
 ed="X" n="0436a23"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930a08"/>騖驟。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">頓除妄宰空不生華漸竭愛源金無重鑛。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0436a24"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930a09"/><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">理絕修<pb ed="X" id="X10.0256.0436b" n="0436b"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0436b01"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930a10"/>證智似階差覺前前非名後後位況妄忘起滅德等<lb
 ed="X" n="0436b02"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930a11"/>圓明者焉。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">然出廐良駒已搖鞭影。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">薶塵大寶須設治方。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">故三觀澄明真假俱入。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">諸輪綺互單複圓修。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">四相潛神非覺違拒四病出<lb
 ed="X" n="0436b10"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930b01"/>體心華發明。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">復令長中下期。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">克念攝念而加行。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">別徧互習業障惑障<lb
 ed="X" n="0436b13"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930b04"/>而銷亡成就慧身靜極覺徧百千世界佛境現前。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">是以聞五種名超剎寶施福<lb
 ed="X" n="0436b16"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930b07"/>說半偈義勝河沙小乘實由無法不持無機不被者<lb
 ed="X" n="0436b17"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930b08"/>也。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">噫巴歌和眾似量騰於猿心<lb
 ed="X" n="0436b19"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930b10"/>雪曲應稀了義匿於龍藏。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">宗密髫專<lb
 ed="X" n="0436b22"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930b13"/>魯誥冠討竺墳俱溺筌󱇮唯味糟粕。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">幸於涪上針芥相投。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">禪遇南宗教逢斯典。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0436c02"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0930b17"/><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">一言之下心地開通一軸之中義天朗耀。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">頃以道非常道諸行無常今知心是佛心定<lb
 ed="X" n="0436c05"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931a02"/>當作佛。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">然<lb
 ed="X" n="0436c06"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931a03"/>佛稱種智修假多聞故復行詣百城坐探群籍。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">講雖濫泰學且師安。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">叨沐猶<lb
 ed="X" n="0436c12"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931a09"/>吾之納謬當真子之印。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">再逢親友<lb
 ed="X" n="0436c17"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931a14"/>彌感佛恩久慨孤貧將陳法施。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">採集般若綸貫華嚴提挈毗尼發明唯識。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">然醫方萬品宜選對治<lb
 ed="X" n="0436c24"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931b03"/>海寶千般先求如意。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">觀夫文富義博誠讓雜華指體投機無<lb
 ed="X" n="0437a02"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931b05"/>偕圓覺。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">故參詳諸論反復百家以利其器方為疏<lb
 ed="X" n="0437a04"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931b07"/>解。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">冥心<lb
 ed="X" n="0437a06"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931b09"/>聖旨極思研精義備性相禪兼頓漸勒成三卷。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">以<lb
 ed="X" n="0437a07"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931b10"/>傳強學。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">然上中下品根欲性殊<lb
 ed="X" n="0437a09"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931b12"/>令將法彼曲成從其易簡更搜精要直注本經。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div><div type='orig' level='3'><ab type="prose">庶即事即心日益日<lb
 ed="X" n="0437a13"/><lb
 ed="R015" n="0931b16"/>損者矣。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='3'><ab type="prose">。</ab></div></div></div>
</body></text></TEI>